liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: There are reports the first group of injured evacuees from Gaza have entered Egypt via ambulances through the Rafah crossing, according to Reuters and AFP. They both quote Egyptian officials. Meanwhile, Egypt has set up makeshift field hospitals for the injured in  Sheikh Zuweid near Al-Arish:
liveBlogPostPrepared.title: First injured Gazan evacuees enter Egypt: media reports

children.content: There are reports the first group of injured evacuees from Gaza have entered Egypt via ambulances through the Rafah crossing, according to Reuters and AFP.
Meanwhile, Egypt has set up makeshift field hospitals for the injured in  Sheikh Zuweid near Al-Arish:

props.alt: White pop up tents as field hospitals

children.content: Field hospitals will treat injured Gazans in Egypt.

props.alt: Photo inside a pop up tent with blankets on the ground

children.content: Inside the field hospitals for injured Gazans.
